name: "Something is about to take off, very near to your house"
description:
"So I called you, to hear your voice and know that we are burning worlds of paper... I saw you near the house, descending to the woods..."

Video Montage - 2021.

this is the second "mini video" of a series of visual stories involving the "girl in the red dress" and myself, Lautaro Quiroga, as a character of this metaverse.
